snippet.title: Combat Spec Ops - Announce Trailer
snippet.description: First glimpse at Combat Spec Ops, a fresh take on classic multiplayer gameplay featuring multiple game modes including Deathmatch, Team Deathmatch, Free for All, Elimination, Bomb Disposal and more!
